        <p class="ml-2">
            I am currently a student at Cal Poly in San Louis Obispo, where I am majoring in Computer Science.
            I was born and grew up in Seattle, Washington, where I attended Roosevelt High School and earned Eagle Scout in Troop 186.
            My interests include swimming, climbing, and software development.
        </p>

        <h3 class="title"><span class="fa fa-table-tennis mr-2"></span>Experiance</h3>
        <p class="ml-2">
            In the summer of 2016 I interned at the MacCoss Lab, where I worked on the Skyline Team, a software tool for targeted mass spectrometry.
